title: List of International Organization for Standardization standards, 5000-7999
text:
This is a list of published <a href="International%20Organization%20for%20Standardization">International Organization for Standardization</a> (ISO) <a href="standardization">standards</a> and other deliverables. For a complete and up-to-date list of all the ISO standards, see the ISO catalogue.
The standards are protected by <a href="copyright">copyright</a> and most of them must be purchased. However, about 300 of the standards produced by ISO and <a href="International%20Electrotechnical%20Commission">IEC</a>'s Joint Technical Committee 1 (<a href="ISO/IEC%20JTC1">JTC1</a>) have been made freely and publicly available.
